<p><br>
Opal is software for aligning multiple biological sequences.
<p>
In benchmark tests, Opal aligns sequences with good accuracy. On DNA, 
accuracy is similar to that of MAFTT and Muscle; on protein, accuracy is 
similar to MAFFT, and better than Muscle. 
Details of the software are available in this 
<a href="http://bioinformatics.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/content/full/23/13/i559?RESULTFORMAT=&fulltext" target="_blank">paper</a> 
(from the Proceedings of ISMB 2007). 

<p>


